Author: Scarlet_Flames2
Text: Yep, I went to a therapist two weeks ago to try recovering before I was ready. I kind of feel like this is the most ready I’ll ever feel, y’know? I feel like, while one is in the depths of the disorder, it’s impossible to feel 100% ready

Author: roastedpepper
Text: Same boat. Been seeing my therapist for 2 months and still not making real progress. But also just wanted to say I cracked up at “lack toast in toddler ants”. LOL!
